title: Malia Obama is spotted outside Weinstein Company offices | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Back to the grindstone! Malia Obama is spotted outside Weinstein offices and running errands as she returns to her internship after a long weekend partying at a NYC club and in Aspen Malia Obama was spotted walking into work at the Weinstein Company's Tribeca offices on Tuesday, wearing a denim skirt, shearling jacket and a beanie After work she ran errands and was spotted at the bargain beauty store Ricky's The former first daughter was seen in the VIP section of the bar Up&Down in Manhattan's Meatpacking district on Friday before she headed to Colorado On Sunday, Malia enjoyed lunch in Aspen on Sunday at Cloud Nine Bistro while skiing with a group of friends She was with the children of New York Giants chairman Steve Tisch, daughter of billionaire Bobby Kotick, and Diane von Furstenberg's grandson Tassilo Fashion designer Monique Lhuillier, a favorite of Malia's mom Michelle while in the White House, was also in attendance and posted a photo of the group Outside, close to 100 people gathered for a daytime dance party while spraying over 200 bottles of Veuve Clicquot champagne, which are sold for $125 each Published: 10:13 GMT, 22 February 2017 | Updated: 15:29 GMT, 22 February 2017 234 shares
